Class SerializerCore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.numenta.nupic.serialize.SerializerCore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Persistable

    public class SerializerCore
extends java.lang.Object
implements Persistable
    PeristenceAPI underbelly which uses the FST Fast Serialization library to serialize various HTM.java object.

    cogmission
